SafeChat-Server is server software required by the SafeChat client.

SafeChat-Server Built Requirements:
GNU Make
GNU C++ Compiler (g++)

Build Instructions:
"Cd" to the folder containing the makefile and main.cpp.
Enter "make build" to compile.
Enter "sudo make install" to install SafeChat-Server to /usr/bin/.
Enter "safechat-server --help" to view the required flags (these flags only need to be provided once, as SafeChat-Server saves the last used preferences).